## 6. 数据模型（核心）

### 6.1 用户实体
```
User {
  user_id: INT PK
  openid: VARCHAR(28) UNIQUE
  nickname: VARCHAR(32)
  phone: VARCHAR(11)
  avatar: VARCHAR(255)
  member_level: TINYINT DEFAULT 0
  member_points: INT DEFAULT 0
  status: TINYINT DEFAULT 1
  created_at: TIMESTAMP
}
```

### 6.2 宠物实体
```
Pet {
  pet_id: INT PK
  user_id: INT FK
  name: VARCHAR(32)
  breed: VARCHAR(50)
  breed_type: ENUM('tiny','small','medium','large','giant')
  birth_date: DATE
  gender: TINYINT
  weight: DECIMAL(4,1)
  tags: JSON
  is_default: BOOLEAN
}
```

### 6.3 路线实体
```
Route {
  route_id: INT PK
  route_no: VARCHAR(20) UNIQUE
  name: VARCHAR(100)
  route_type: TINYINT
  title: VARCHAR(50)
  subtitle: VARCHAR(100)
  description: TEXT
  base_price: DECIMAL(10,2)
  min_participants: INT
  max_participants: INT
  difficulty: TINYINT
  suitable_breeds: JSON
  status: TINYINT
}
```

### 6.4 订单实体
```
Order {
  order_id: INT PK
  order_no: VARCHAR(20) UNIQUE
  user_id: INT FK
  schedule_id: INT FK
  route_id: INT FK
  participant_count: INT
  pet_count: INT
  total_amount: DECIMAL(10,2)
  pay_amount: DECIMAL(10,2)
  status: TINYINT
  paid_at: TIMESTAMP NULL
}
```

